                                                                                            <p class="word-copy-lh-mb" style="margin-bottom:12.0pt;"><a href="https://www.instagram.com/hunterliguore/" title="https://www.instagram.com/hunterliguore/"><strong>Hunter Liguore</strong></a>&nbsp;is the author of <em>The Modern Art of War: Sun Tzu’s Hidden Path to Peace and Wholeness</em>, now translated into five languages. She’s undertaken critical research in peace and social justice studies. A regular columnist for <em>Spirituality &amp; Healt</em>h&nbsp;magazine, she is a professor of writing, communications, and art history in New England.</p>
